@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About";
}
<h2>@ViewData["Title"].</h2>
<h3>@ViewData["Message"]</h3>

<p>DDCA is a B2B company that offer its services to servica companies that are using drones to perform their operations. We do the technological heavy lifting for the companies so they can focus on what the do best which is flying and communicating with their customers. Our devices can be mounted on any drone and can accept many different sensors that can be programmed depending on the especific need of the costumers</p>

<div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" data-interval="6000">
    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="3"></li>
    </ol>
    <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
        <div class="item active">
            <img src="~/images/banner1.png" alt="Drones in construction sites" class="img-responsive" />
            <div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
                <p>
                    Use drones to get a bird view of all the assets and personnel in a construction site.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/images/banner2.png" alt="Drones in solar fields" class="img-responsive" />
            <div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
                <p>
                    Make a quick and reliable diagnostic of the solar panels using termography imaginery
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/images/banner3.png" alt="Drones in GSM tower inspection" class="img-responsive" />
            <div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
                <p>
                    Create a 3D map of the signal streng in the space and use drones to inspect high towers.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/images/banner4.png" alt="Drones in agriculture" class="img-responsive" />
            <div class="carousel-caption" role="option">
                <p>
                    Get detailed data of the composition of the soil and the health of the crops.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
</div>